---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import IeltsAppImage from "../../assets/IELTS-app.png";
import IeltsBannerImage from "../../assets/IELTS-banners.gif";
import IeltsDesktopImage from "../../assets/IELTS-desktop.png";
import IeltsSetUpGuideImage from "../../assets/IELTS-set-up-guide.gif";
---

<Layout>
    <article class="post">
        <div class="post--header">
            <div class="post--date">October 2021</div>
            <h1>Ask forgiveness not permission</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="post--body">
            <p>
                At the start of last year the British Council pitched to IELTS -
                its International English Language Testing partners, an ambition
                to develop the first product that fully aligned language
                learning with testing.
            </p>
            <p>
                With the vast majority of it's global teaching and testing
                centres closed, the organisation felt it had an opportunity to
                develop an offer that benefitted the increasing number of
                digital natives with accessible enabling technology.
            </p>
            <p>
                The decision was made to invite Senior Leadership to engage in a
                conversation about the opportunity, for which a significant
                number of discussion aids needed to be prepared.
            </p>

             <div class="caption">
                    <Image src={IeltsSetUpGuideImage} alt="" />
                    <p>Mobile wireframe for test set-up explanation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="caption">
                <Image class="fullwidth" src={IeltsDesktopImage} alt="" />

                <p>Desktop wireframe for English practise homepage.</p>

                <div class="caption">
                    <Image class="fullwidth" src={IeltsAppImage} alt="" />
                    <p>Mobile mock-ups for the self-paced learning app.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="caption">
                    <Image src={IeltsBannerImage} alt="" />
                    <p>Audience segmented promotions for social media.</p>
                </div>

